# Python UV Setup

Use `uv` for all Python project setup and dependency management.

## New Projects

```bash
mkdir my-project && cd my-project
uv init
uv venv
```

## Dependencies

```bash
uv add requests           # Add dependency
uv add --dev pytest       # Dev dependency
uv sync                   # Install all
```

## Running Code

