## pyproject.toml

```toml
[project]
name = "my-project"
version = "0.1.0"
requires-python = ">=3.12"
dependencies = []

[build-system]
requires = ["hatchling"]
build-backend = "hatchling.build"
```

## Notes

- Faster than pip, better resolution
- Commit `uv.lock` for reproducible builds
- No venv activation needed
